      "Player slots 1 and 2 are leads.",
      "Player slots 3 and 4 are backline.",
      "Gender and PP are intentionally excluded.",
      "Actual used moves and targets must be derived from the central battle text, not from cursor position.",
      "Move effectiveness shown in the UI is an observed hint only; target-specific interpretation belongs to a later inference layer."
